preqs: Students must have passed ETF2100 or ETC2410 or must be enrolled in Course Code 3822 or 4412

rules.ruleString: Must have passed 1 (I/W) units in {ETF2100, ETX2121} with grades other than {STANDARD-DEF, STANDARD-NS}
For COURSE_CODE NOT IN {3822, 4412} Do Must have passed an (I/W) unit in {ETC2410, ETF2100} Otherwise true

description: The topics covered in this unit include: review of regression analysis, binomial dependent variables, unordered multinomial dependent variables, ordered multinomial dependent variables, duration dependent variables.  Computer software EVIEWS will be used to apply these techniques to real world problems.
